data.description: Have you always wanted to own a Mountain Cabin?  Well, now is your chance.  This 2 bedroom, 2 bath homes has 1280 sq ft, an open floor plan, pellet store in living room, vaulted ceilings, knotty pine throughout and its log sided! This home has a new hot water heater and a new roof was installed July 2023. You'll love the covered front & back decks, the raised gardens and the fenced back yard.  Inside the large 1 car garage is a shop and finished loft.
